        "username": "prakash"
      },
      "date": "2012-10-25 16:56:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe Maloo failure hit an assertion:\n\n\n    20:09:37:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: == sanityn test 16: 2500 iterations of dual-mount fsx == 20:09:32 (1351134572)\n    20:09:37:LustreError: 20294:0:(lov_lock.c:835:lov_lock_wait()) ASSERTION( sub != ((void *)0) ) failed:\n    20:09:37:LustreError: 20294:0:(lov_lock.c:835:lov_lock_wait()) LBUG\n    20:09:37:Pid: 20294, comm: fsx \n    20:09:37:\n    20:09:37:Call Trace:\n    20:09:37: [<ffffffffa0b6b905>] libcfs_debug_dumpstack+0x55/0x80 [libcfs]\n    20:09:37: [<ffffffffa0b6bf17>] lbug_with_loc+0x47/0xb0 [libcfs]\n    20:09:37: [<ffffffffa0792eb2>] lov_lock_wait+0x252/0x2a0 [lov]\n    20:09:37: [<ffffffffa0c4c185>] ? cl_env_info+0x15/0x20 [obdclass]\n    20:09:37: [<ffffffffa0c55c75>] cl_wait_try+0xe5/0x310 [obdclass]\n    20:09:37: [<ffffffffa0c59da5>] cl_wait+0x65/0x270 [obdclass]\n    20:09:37: [<ffffffffa0957b64>] cl_glimpse_lock+0x1b4/0x4a0 [lustre]\n    20:09:37: [<ffffffffa09583b7>] cl_glimpse_size0+0x187/0x190 [lustre]\n    20:09:37: [<ffffffffa0909948>] ll_file_seek+0x268/0x2d0 [lustre]\n    20:09:37: [<ffffffff81179d5a>] vfs_llseek+0x3a/0x40\n    20:09:37: [<ffffffff8117b516>] sys_lseek+0x66/0x80\n    20:09:37: [<ffffffff8100b0f2>] system_call_fastpath+0x16/0x1b\n\nI'm inclined to think this patch caused it.",
