          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-2030 clio: release sublocks held partly in lov_lock_enqueue",
        "message": "LU-2030 clio: release sublocks held partly in lov_lock_enqueue\n\nin lov_lock_enqueue, if there are some sublocks with CLS_HELD state\nwhile some other sublocks are still wating for server to grant,\nthen drop the reference of these CLS_HELD sublocks before return,\nwhich can cause the eviction if one of these sublocks take too\nmuch time to acquire the permission from server.\n\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I25872f236a1f4f3c7a2e55f19bd5aa900657258c\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
